      --json         Emit machine-readable JSON (the node object, or `null` on a miss with a non-zero exit). The JSON shape is unstable and may change before 0.2
      --repo <REPO>  Path to the repository. Ignored by `init` when it is given its own PATH argument [default: .]
  -h, --help         Print help

